    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Project-wide manifest of which models ship in the build. Stores a thin name -&gt; { type, registration } list; catalog metadata stays server-owned and is read via ListModels. The Model Manager window writes it; component pickers and a future packaging step read it.</para>
<para>Persisted to &lt;YourProject&gt;/Config/DefaultGame.ini under [/Script/TryllClient.TryllModelManifest]. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
